  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     Word Embeddings
Category:    Representation
Definition:  Dense vectors where semantic similarity = vector proximity
Year:        2013
Researchers: Mikolov et al.
Applications:NLP, recommendation, search
Related:     Word2Vec, GloVe, BERT embeddings

Concept:     GAN
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Generator vs discriminator adversarial training
Year:        2014
Researchers: Ian Goodfellow et al.
Applications:Image synthesis, deepfakes, augmentation
Related:     Mode collapse, discriminator, generator

Concept:     Diffusion Model
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Learns to reverse a noise-adding process for generation
Year:        2020
Researchers: Ho et al.
Applications:Image/video/audio generation (Stable Diffusion)
Related:     DDPM, score matching, noise schedule

============================================================
  ECONOMICS
============================================================

Concept:    Market Failure
Category:   Microeconomics
Definition: Free markets fail to allocate resources efficiently
Formula:    Social cost = private + external cost
Economist:  Arthur Pigou
Example:    Carbon emissions: negative externality requiring government intervention

Concept:    Compound Interest
Category:   Finance
Definition: Interest calculated on initial principal and accumulated interest
Formula:    A = P(1 + r/n)^(nt)
Economist:  Various
Example:    Einstein allegedly called it the 8th wonder of the world

Concept:    Elasticity
Category:   Microeconomics
Definition: Responsiveness of demand to price change
Formula:    PED = %dQd / %dP
Economist:  Alfred Marshall
Example:    Gasoline demand inelastic; luxury goods elastic

